item.title: Imperial’s Volleyball club is served sweet sucess this year
item.author: Imperial College Volleyball Club,
item.description: The start of the year already hinted at a great volleyball season to come; with over 120 people attending the taster session and a record-high membership of 87. After an absence of two years, the women’s BUCS team returned to the first division for the 2014-15 season. Throughout the season the …
